                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿رَجْعٌ بَعِيدٌ﴾ رُجُوعٌ إِلَى الحَيَاةِ بَعْدَ المَوْتِ، بَعِيدُ الوُقُوعِ.</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "50:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَنْقُصُ﴾ تُفْنِي مِنْ أَجْسَادِهِمْ.</h2>\n<p>﴿كِتَابٌ حَفِيظٌ﴾ حَافِظٌ لِجَمِيعِ أَفْعَالِهِمْ؛ وَهُوَ اللَّوْحُ المَحْفُوظُ.</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "50:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مَرِيجٍ﴾ مُضْطَرِبٍ، مُخْتَلَطٍ، لاَ يَثْبُتُونَ عَلَى شَيْءٍ.</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "50:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فُرُوجٍ﴾ فُتُوقٍ، وَشُقُوقٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "50:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَدَدْنَاهَا﴾ وَسَّعْنَاهَا، وَفَرَشْنَاهَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿رَوَاسِيَ﴾ جِبَالاً ثَوَابِتَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿زَوْجٍ بَهِيجٍ﴾ نَوْعٍ حَسَنِ المَنْظَرِ.</h2>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "50:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تَبْصِرَةً﴾ عِبْرَةً يَتَبَصَّرُ بِهَا مِنْ عَمَى الجَهْلِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿مُنِيبٍ﴾ رَجَّاعٍ إِلَى اللهِ تَعَالَى.</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "50:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَحَبَّ الْحَصِيدِ﴾ حَبَّ الزَّرْعِ الَّذِي يُحْصَدُ.</h2>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "50:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بَاسِقَاتٍ﴾ طِوَالاً.</h2>\n<h2>﴿طَلْعٌ نَضِيدٌ﴾ ثَمَرٌ مُتَرَاكِبٌ بَعْضُهُ فَوْقَ بَعْضٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
